PN,44401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FA "seismic political shift" following
OL,7,Flast week's elections has been hailed
OL,8,Fas exciting by Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Ffirst minister.
OL,11,FMichelle O'Neill was speaking after
OL,12,Fthe Scottish National Party and Plaid
OL,13,FCymru topped the polls in Scotland and
OL,14,FWales.
OL,16,FShe said that she and Sinn Fein
OL,17,Fpresident Mary-Lou McDonald have
OL,18,Fspoken with Scottish First Minister
OL,19,FJohn Swinney and Plaid Cymru's Rhun ap
OL,20,FIorwerth who is set to become first
OL,21,Fminister of Wales.
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@[O]xD@]rr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FShe said they spoke of "the potential
OL,7,Fthat we have to find the common ground
OL,8,Fto work together to build towards a
OL,9,Fbrighter, better future for our
OL,10,Frespective people".
OL,12,F"We have had a seismic political shift
OL,13,Fin terms of the outcome of the
OL,14,Felection," she told reporters in
OL,15,FParliament Buildings in Belfast on
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,18,F"I think it's quite an exciting
OL,19,Fjuncture, the very first time we have
OL,20,Fnationalist first ministers in
OL,21,FScotland, Wales and here with myself.
OL,26,@nD@XOUrD@RO]tD@AOUvD@JO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,F"I think that is quite an exciting
OL,7,Fjourney in terms of where we pivot to
OL,8,Fnext.
OL,10,F"We want better for our people, we
OL,11,Fwant a better arrangement for our
OL,12,Fpeople, and we have committed to work
OL,13,Ftogether on that common ground, to
OL,14,Fwork out how we can bring about
OL,15,Fpositive change for our people, and at
OL,16,Fthe core of that change is about
OL,17,Findependence for our people, free from
OL,18,Fthe limitations of Westminster, free
OL,19,Ffrom the disregard from Westminster
OL,20,Fand towards a bright, more positive
OL,21,Ffuture."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FSDLP leader Claire Hanna said the UK
OL,7,Fis "changing substantially", adding
OL,8,Fher party is determined that Northern
OL,9,FIreland "won't just be a passenger in
OL,10,Fthat".
OL,12,F"The symbolism of the first ministers
OL,13,Fis significant, but we've got to use
OL,14,Fthe power that we have here, and we've
OL,15,Fgot to do the work of persuasion," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@[O]qD@IOUrD@EO]tD@AOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FHowever, she also pointed out that
OL,7,F"symbolism doesn't put bread on
OL,8,Fanyone's table", and emphasised the
OL,9,Fneed to "use power responsibly and
OL,10,Fchange people's lives", adding her
OL,11,Fparty in Opposition is "working every
OL,12,Fday" to press ministers in terms of
OL,13,Ftheir responsibilities.
OL,15,FHowever, DUP leader Gavin Robinson
OL,16,Fdismissed the view, describing a vote
OL,17,Fagainst Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,18,FStarmer, and not for the dismantling
OL,19,Fof the United Kingdom.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]qD@IOUrD@VO]sD@XOUtD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FHe also described "two and a half"
OL,7,Fnationalist first ministers, referring
OL,8,Fto the joint office at Stormont shared
OL,9,Fby his colleague Emma Little-Pengelly.
OL,11,F"The First Minister of Northern
OL,12,FIreland is in a joint office with this
OL,13,Funionist," he said, motioning towards
OL,14,FMs Little-Pengelly standing beside him.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@bO]sD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,F"Nothing has changed, Scotland had a
OL,7,FFirst Minister that believed in
OL,8,FScottish independence last week, and
OL,9,Fthe week before, votes for nationalism
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland have not increased
OL,11,Fby one iota in percentage terms since
OL,12,F1998.
OL,14,F"More importantly, right throughout
OL,15,Fthe United Kingdom, unionist parties
OL,16,Fgot more votes than anywhere else, and
OL,17,Fanybody else in the elections last
OL,18,Fweek."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FHe added: "People in Scotland were
OL,7,Fvoting against Keir Starmer, not the
OL,8,Funion, people in Wales were voting
OL,9,Fagainst Keir Starmer, not against the
OL,10,Funion, and when we get our chance,
OL,11,Fpeople in Northern Ireland have their
OL,12,Fsay next year, I guarantee that
OL,13,Funionism will win that election, and
OL,14,Fif unionists can bring themselves to
OL,15,Fco-operate they will win in a way that
OL,16,Fcannot be ignored."
OL,18,FMeanwhile Alliance Party leader Naomi
OL,19,FLong said it is "clear that people are
OL,20,Ffed up with politics", across the
OL,21,Fworld.
OL,26,@nD@KOUxD@SO]{D@QOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,FShe called for reform of political
OL,7,Fsystems, and particularly criticised
OL,8,Fthe first-past-the-post election
OL,9,Fsystem as "biased towards extreme
OL,10,Fviews", adding it "doesn't give the
OL,11,Fnarrative of the majority".
OL,13,F"We need to reset the dial.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@FO]rD@SOUsD@ZO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
