FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778609470
OL,3,CNI first minister excited by 'seismic
OL,4,Cpolitical shift' across UK
OL,6,F"People are not wrong to be frustrated
OL,7,Fat politics, though I may not agree at
OL,8,Fhow they express their frustration, if
OL,9,Fwe as politicians don't step up and
OL,10,Fmake the difference that is required,
OL,11,Fthe public are going to make a
OL,12,Fdifference, whether that's a
OL,13,Fdifference that will lead to better
OL,14,Foutcomes for them, I think is highly
OL,15,Fquestionable," she said.
